metadata.name: Boy That Cried Wolf
metadata.description:
One day he shouted for help, the wolf did not appear.
He lied about it

Next day he shouted for help, the wolf did not appear.
He lied about it.

The other next day he shouted for help, the wolf did appear.
No one helps him.

"Even he tells the truth, no one believe him."

Lesson learned.
.
.

by ICHIREN 2022
